summary: “It’s also obvious that the stab ignites some feelings she has never felt before. It shows in the scene she soothes Gabriel. It...
caption: “It’s also obvious that the stab ignites some feelings she has never felt before. It shows in the scene she soothes Gabriel. It looks like she really feels sorry for him, not just fake it. After she’s done what she thinks it would help Gabriel. Her facial impression vividly shows confusion. She feels something but she doesn’t know what it is. We see her always take pleasure from watching people slowly die, but with Gabriel, I don’t see any of those feelings and she does it as fastest and least painful as possible.”  (x)
